        "text_PJxJEe": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h3>You have the Queen of Wands in your hands because it is finally time to fully inhabit your presence. This card comes to those stepping into visibility, influence, or leadership, whether personally or professionally.<\/h3><h3>You may already feel a growing confidence or a desire to express yourself more openly. At the same time, you might still hesitate, worrying about being too much or standing out. <\/h3><h3>You can dissolve that hesitation. Real confidence does not reside in loudness. Your energy naturally inspires others when you stop dimming it. Your warmth and leadership is meant to be shared and adored.<\/h3><h3>The Queen of Wands could also mean that your boundaries are strengthening. You are learning what deserves your energy and what does not. You are honouring yourself, and in time, others will respond to that. <br\/><br\/>On Love<\/h3><p>Your energy is magnetic and by showing up even when you don’t want to, you could attract passionate, aligned connections. You will be seen for who you really are. <\/p><h3>On Health<\/h3><p>The more you honour your boundaries, the longer you honour your need to rest, you will increase your own vitality. <\/p><h3>On Money \/ Career<\/h3><p>There could be ample opportunities for leadership, more responsibility, public recognition. This year will be one of high visibility. You are ready for this challenge.<\/p><h3>How to work with this energy<\/h3><p>You must own your presence. You must lead without shrinking who you are. Speak up, and don’t back down.<br\/><br\/>Recommended products<\/p><ol><li>Sunday Rituals Hair Repair & Growth Oil – Confidence from the roots<\/li><li>Festive Cherry Bag Charm (Cherry) – Bold feminine energy<\/li><li>Cross Braided Essentials Handbag – Wine Edition<\/li><\/ol><p>You can find these in our pop-up booth at Night At Orchard, along the outdoor pathway between Ngee Ann City & Ion Orchard between 26-28 Dec, 3pm onwards <\/p>",
            "text_size": "typeset2",
            "secondary_color": false,
            "enable_highlight": false,
            "highlight_style": "marker"
          }
        },
